[{"id":"VH902641","type":"mcq","stimulusHtml":"<p class=\"stem_paragraph\">Below is an attempt to derive the derivative of <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"the secant of x\"><math alttext=\"the secant of x\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mstyle><mrow><mi>sec</mi><mo>⁡</mo><mi>x</mi></mrow></mstyle></math></span></span> using the product rule, where <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"x\"><math alttext=\"x\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mstyle><mrow><mi>x</mi></mrow></mstyle></math></span></span> is in the domain of <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"the secant of x\"><math alttext=\"the secant of x\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mstyle><mrow><mi>sec</mi><mo>⁡</mo><mi>x</mi></mrow></mstyle></math></span></span>. In which step, if any, does an error first appear?</p><ul class=\"unordered_list style:2\"><li class=\"list_paragraph\">Step 1: <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"the secant of x, times the cosine of x, equals 1\"><math alttext=\"the secant of x, times the cosine of x, equals 1\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mstyle><mrow><mi>sec</mi><mo>⁡</mo><mi>x</mi><mo>⋅</mo><mi>cos</mi><mo>⁡</mo><mi>x</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow></mstyle></math></span></span></li><li class=\"list_paragraph\">Step 2: <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"the derivative, with respect to x, of, open parenthesis, the secant of x, times the cosine of x, close parenthesis, equals 0\"><math alttext=\"the derivative, with respect to x, of, open parenthesis, the secant of x, times the cosine of x, close parenthesis, equals 0\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mstyle><mrow><mrow><mfrac><mrow><mo>ⅆ</mo></mrow><mrow><mo>ⅆ</mo><mi>x</mi></mrow></mfrac></mrow><mrow><mo>(</mo><mi>sec</mi><mo>⁡</mo><mi>x</mi><mo>⋅</mo><mi>cos</mi><mo>⁡</mo><mi>x</mi><mo>)</mo></mrow><mo>=</mo><mn>0</mn></mrow></mstyle></math></span></span></li><li class=\"list_paragraph\">Step 3: <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"the derivative, with respect to x, of, open parenthesis, the secant of x, close parenthesis, times, the cosine of x, minus the secant of x, times the sine of x, equals 0\"><math alttext=\"the derivative, with respect to x, of, open parenthesis, the secant of x, close parenthesis, times, the cosine of x, minus the secant of x, times the sine of x, equals 0\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mstyle><mrow><mrow><mfrac><mrow><mo>ⅆ</mo></mrow><mrow><mo>ⅆ</mo><mi>x</mi></mrow></mfrac></mrow><mrow><mo>(</mo><mi>sec</mi><mo>⁡</mo><mi>x</mi><mo>)</mo></mrow><mo>⋅</mo><mi>cos</mi><mo>⁡</mo><mi>x</mi><mo>−</mo><mi>sec</mi><mo>⁡</mo><mi>x</mi><mo>⋅</mo><mi>sin</mi><mo>⁡</mo><mi>x</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>0</mn></mrow></mstyle></math></span></span></li><li class=\"list_paragraph\">Step 4: <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"the derivative, with respect to x, of the secant of x, equals, the fraction with numerator, the secant of x, times the sine of x, and denominator the cosine of x, which equals, the secant of x times the fraction, the sine of x, over the cosine of x, which equals, the secant of x, times the tangent of x\"><math alttext=\"the derivative, with respect to x, of the secant of x, equals, the fraction with numerator, the secant of x, times the sine of x, and denominator the cosine of x, which equals, the secant of x times the fraction, the sine of x, over the cosine of x, which equals, the secant of x, times the tangent of x\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mstyle><mrow><mrow><mfrac><mrow><mo>ⅆ</mo></mrow><mrow><mo>ⅆ</mo><mi>x</mi></mrow></mfrac></mrow><mrow><mo>(</mo><mi>sec</mi><mo>⁡</mo><mi>x</mi><mo>)</mo></mrow><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mrow><mi>sec</mi><mo>⁡</mo><mi>x</mi><mo>⋅</mo><mi>sin</mi><mo>⁡</mo><mi>x</mi></mrow><mrow><mi>cos</mi><mo>⁡</mo><mi>x</mi></mrow></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mi>sec</mi><mo>⁡</mo><mi>x</mi><mo>⋅</mo><mfrac><mrow><mi>sin</mi><mo>⁡</mo><mi>x</mi></mrow><mrow><mi>cos</mi><mo>⁡</mo><mi>x</mi></mrow></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mi>sec</mi><mo>⁡</mo><mi>x</mi><mo>⋅</mo><mi>tan</mi><mo>⁡</mo><mi>x</mi></mrow></mstyle></math></span></span></li></ul>\n","rubricRef":"VH902641_rubric","choicesHtml":["<p class=\"choice_paragraph\">Step 1</p>","<p class=\"choice_paragraph\">Step 2</p>","<p class=\"choice_paragraph\">Step 3</p>","<p class=\"choice_paragraph\">There is no error.</p>"],"answer":3}]